{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782357965371,"sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_E3AWfNQrN3Z3mzko6RQcqIBG","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\ArkData\\cj-apis-preferences\\ohosdatapreferences用户首选项\\class_Preferences\\static_func_getPr_2more_c22d3d6a.md"},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\ArkData\\cj-apis-preferences\\ohosdatapreferences用户首选项\\class_Preferences\\static_func_getPr_2more_c22d3d6a.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ### static func getPreferences(UIAbilityContext, PreferencesOptions)\n2: \n3: ```cangjie\n4: public static func getPreferences(context: UIAbilityContext, options: PreferencesOptions): Preferences\n5: ```\n6: \n7: **功能：** 获取Preferences实例。\n8: \n9: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.DistributedDataManager.Preferences.Core\n10: \n11: **起始版本：** 22\n12: \n13: **参数：**\n14: \n15: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n16: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n17: |context|[UIAbilityContext](../AbilityKit/cj-apis-app-ability-ui_ability.md#class-uiabilitycontext)|是|-|应用上下文。|\n18: |options|[PreferencesOptions](#class-preferencesoptions)|是|-|与Preferences实例相关的配置选项。|\n19: \n20: **返回值：**\n21: \n22: |类型|说明|\n23: |:----|:----|\n24: |[Preferences](#class-preferences)|返回Preferences实例。|\n25: \n26: **异常：**\n27: \n28: - BusinessException：对应错误码如下表，详见[通用错误码](../cj-errorcode-universal.md)和[用户首选项错误码](./cj-errorcode-preferences.md)。\n29: \n30:   | 错误码ID | 错误信息 |\n31:   | :---- | :--- |\n32:   | 801 | Capability not supported. |\n33:   | 15500000 | Inner error. |\n34:   | 15501001 | The operations is supported in stage mode only. |\n35:   | 15501002 | Invalid dataGroupId. |\n36: \n37: **示例：**\n38: \n39: <!-- compile only -->\n40: <!-- compile -->\n41: \n42: ```cangjie\n43: // index.cj\n44: \n45: import kit.ArkData.*\n46: import ohos.business_exception.BusinessException\n47: import kit.PerformanceAnalysisKit.Hilog\n48: \n49: try {\n50:     let preferences = Preferences.getPreferences(Global.abilityContext, PreferencesOptions(\"mystore\", dataGroupId:\"myGroupID\")) // 此处需手动配置模板，获取Context上下文。上下文获取方式请参见使用说明。\n51:     // 删除 Preferences 实例的缓存\n52:     Preferences.removePreferencesFromCache(Global.abilityContext, PreferencesOptions(\"mystore\", dataGroupId:\"myGroupID\"))\n53: } catch (e: BusinessException) {\n54:     Hilog.info(0, \"test\", \"${e.message}\")\n55: }\n56: ```\n57: \n58: ### static func removePreferencesFromCache(UIAbilityContext, String)\n59: \n60: ```cangjie\n61: public static func removePreferencesFromCache(context: UIAbilityContext, name: String): Unit\n62: ```\n63: \n64: **功能：** 从缓存中移除指定的Preferences实例。\n65: \n66: 应用首次调用[getPreferences](#static-func-getpreferencesuiabilitycontext-string)接口获取某个Preferences实例后，该实例会被缓存起来。后续再次调用getPreferences时，不会再从持久化文件中读取，而是直接从缓存中获取Preferences实例。\n67: \n68: 调用此接口移除缓存中的实例之后，再次调用getPreferences将会重新读取持久化文件，生成新的Preferences实例。\n69: \n70: 调用该接口后，不建议再使用旧的Preferences实例进行数据操作，否则会出现数据一致性问题。\n71: \n72: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.DistributedDataManager.Preferences.Core\n73: \n74: **起始版本：** 22\n75: \n76: **参数：**\n77: \n78: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n79: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n80: |context|[UIAbilityContext](../AbilityKit/cj-apis-app-ability-ui_ability.md#class-uiabilitycontext)|是|-|应用上下文。|\n81: |name|String|是|-|Preferences实例的名称。|\n82: \n83: **异常：**\n84: \n85: - BusinessException：对应错误码如下表，详见[用户首选项错误码](./cj-errorcode-preferences.md)。\n86: \n87:   | 错误码ID | 错误信息 |\n88:   | :---- | :--- |\n89:   | 15500000 | Inner error. |\n90: \n91: **示例：**\n92: \n93: <!-- compile only -->\n94: <!-- compile -->\n95: \n96: ```cangjie\n97: // index.cj\n98: \n99: import kit.ArkData.*\n100: import ohos.business_exception.BusinessException\n101: import kit.PerformanceAnalysisKit.Hilog\n102: \n103: try {\n104:     let preferences = Preferences.getPreferences(Global.abilityContext, PreferencesOptions(\"mystore\", dataGroupId:\"myGroupID\")) // 此处需手动配置模板，获取Context上下文。上下文获取方式请参见使用说明。\n105:     // 删除 Preferences 实例的缓存\n106:     Preferences.removePreferencesFromCache(Global.abilityContext, PreferencesOptions(\"mystore\", dataGroupId:\"myGroupID\"))\n107: } catch (e: BusinessException) {\n108:     Hilog.info(0, \"test\", \"${e.message}\")\n109: }\n110: ```\n\n(End of file - total 110 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"### static func getPreferences(UIAbilityContext, PreferencesOptions)\n\n```cangjie\npublic static func getPreferences(context: UIAbilityContext, options: PreferencesOptions): Preferences\n```\n\n**功能：** 获取Preferences实例。\n\n**系统能力：** SystemCapability.DistributedDataManager.Preferences.Core\n\n**起始版本：** 22\n\n**参数：**\n\n|参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n|:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n|context|[UIAbilityContext](../AbilityKit/cj-apis-app-ability-ui_ability.md#class-uiabilitycontext)|是|-|应用上下文。|\n|options|[PreferencesOptions](#class-preferencesoptions)|是|-|与Preferences实例相关的配置选项。|\n\n**返回值：**","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\ArkData\\cj-apis-preferences\\ohosdatapreferences用户首选项\\class_Preferences\\static_func_getPr_2more_c22d3d6a.md","time":{"start":1782357965360,"end":1782357965370}},"id":"prt_efcd039cf001Sa5vt2hrpm9Zwe","sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","messageID":"msg_efccfd268001R9m8pZE80INWfc"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782357965469,"sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_tiPqcS1p36UQfN4qdCjghsRD","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\ArkData\\cj-apis-preferences\\ohosdatapreferences用户首选项\\class_Preferences\\func_putString_Preferen_e22bc770.md"},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\ArkData\\cj-apis-preferences\\ohosdatapreferences用户首选项\\class_Preferences\\func_putString_Preferen_e22bc770.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ### func put(String, PreferencesValueType)\n2: \n3: ```cangjie\n4: public func put(key: String, value: PreferencesValueType): Unit\n5: ```\n6: \n7: **功能：** 将数据写入缓存的Preferences实例中，可通过[flush](#func-flush)将Preferences实例持久化。\n8: \n9: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.DistributedDataManager.Preferences.Core\n10: \n11: **起始版本：** 22\n12: \n13: **参数：**\n14: \n15: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n16: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n17: |key|String|是|-|要修改的存储的Key，不能为空，最大长度限制为[MAX_KEY_LENGTH](#const-max_key_length)。|\n18: |value|[PreferencesValueType](#enum-preferencesvaluetype)|是|-|存储的新值。支持Int64、Float64、String、Bool、 Array\\<Bool>、Array\\<Float64>、Array\\<String>。|\n19: \n20: **异常：**\n21: \n22: - BusinessException：对应错误码如下表，详见[用户首选项错误码](./cj-errorcode-preferences.md)。\n23: \n24:   | 错误码ID | 错误信息 |\n25:   | :---- | :--- |\n26:   | 15500000 | Inner error. |\n27: \n28: **示例：**\n29: \n30: <!-- compile only -->\n31: <!-- compile -->\n32: \n33: ```cangjie\n34: // index.cj\n35: \n36: import kit.ArkData.*\n37: import ohos.business_exception.BusinessException\n38: import kit.PerformanceAnalysisKit.Hilog\n39: \n40: try {\n41:     var preferences = Preferences.getPreferences(Global.abilityContext, PreferencesOptions(\"mystore\", dataGroupId:\"myGroupID\")) // 此处需手动配置模板，获取Context上下文。上下文获取方式请参见使用说明。\n42:     preferences.put(\"Monday\", PreferencesValueType.StringData(\"今天天气真好\"))\n43: } catch (e: BusinessException) {\n44:     Hilog.info(0, \"test\", \"${e.message}\")\n45: }\n46: ```\n\n(End of file - total 46 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"### func put(String, PreferencesValueType)\n\n```cangjie\npublic func put(key: String, value: PreferencesValueType): Unit\n```\n\n**功能：** 将数据写入缓存的Preferences实例中，可通过[flush](#func-flush)将Preferences实例持久化。\n\n**系统能力：** SystemCapability.DistributedDataManager.Preferences.Core\n\n**起始版本：** 22\n\n**参数：**\n\n|参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n|:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n|key|String|是|-|要修改的存储的Key，不能为空，最大长度限制为[MAX_KEY_LENGTH](#const-max_key_length)。|\n|value|[PreferencesValueType](#enum-preferencesvaluetype)|是|-|存储的新值。支持Int64、Float64、String、Bool、 Array\\<Bool>、Array\\<Float64>、Array\\<String>。|\n\n**异常：**","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\ArkData\\cj-apis-preferences\\ohosdatapreferences用户首选项\\class_Preferences\\func_putString_Preferen_e22bc770.md","time":{"start":1782357965459,"end":1782357965468}},"id":"prt_efcd03a32001QZJHZHCicUzDYR","sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","messageID":"msg_efccfd268001R9m8pZE80INWfc"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782357965598,"sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_DrtIzxzHv13ZDvVOrQHX2Yfq","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\ArkData\\cj-apis-preferences\\ohosdatapreferences用户首选项\\class_Preferences\\func_getString_Pr_2more_0f22f412.md"},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\ArkData\\cj-apis-preferences\\ohosdatapreferences用户首选项\\class_Preferences\\func_getString_Pr_2more_0f22f412.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ### func get(String, PreferencesValueType)\n2: \n3: ```cangjie\n4: public func get(key: String, defValue: PreferencesValueType): PreferencesValueType\n5: ```\n6: \n7: **功能：** 从缓存的Preferences实例中获取键对应的值，如果值为null或者非默认值类型，返回默认数据defValue。\n8: \n9: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.DistributedDataManager.Preferences.Core\n10: \n11: **起始版本：** 22\n12: \n13: **参数：**\n14: \n15: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n16: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n17: |key|String|是|-|要获取的存储Key名称，不能为空，最大长度限制为[MAX_KEY_LENGTH](#const-max_key_length)。|\n18: |defValue|[PreferencesValueType](#enum-preferencesvaluetype)|是|-|默认返回值。支持Int64、Float64、String、Bool、 Array\\<Bool>、Array\\<Float64>、Array\\<String>。|\n19: \n20: **返回值：**\n21: \n22: |类型|说明|\n23: |:----|:----|\n24: |[PreferencesValueType](#enum-preferencesvaluetype)|返回键对应的值。|\n25: \n26: **异常：**\n27: \n28: - BusinessException：对应错误码如下表，详见[用户首选项错误码](./cj-errorcode-preferences.md)。\n29: \n30:   | 错误码ID | 错误信息 |\n31:   | :---- | :--- |\n32:   | 15500000 | Inner error. |\n33: \n34: **示例：**\n35: \n36: <!-- compile only -->\n37: <!-- compile -->\n38: \n39: ```cangjie\n40: // index.cj\n41: \n42: import kit.ArkData.*\n43: import kit.PerformanceAnalysisKit.Hilog\n44: import ohos.business_exception.BusinessException\n45: \n46: try {\n47:     let preferences = Preferences.getPreferences(Global.abilityContext, PreferencesOptions(\"mystore\", dataGroupId:\"myGroupID\")) // 此处需手动配置模板，获取Context上下文。上下文获取方式请参见使用说明。\n48:     var value = preferences.get(\"key\", PreferencesValueType.Integer(0))\n49:     match (value) {\n50:         case PreferencesValueType.Integer(n) => Hilog.info(0, \"AppLogCj\", \"获取到的值为${n}\")\n51:         case _ => Hilog.info(0, \"AppLogCj\", \"获取到的值并不是 Int\")\n52:     }\n53: } catch (e: BusinessException) {\n54:     Hilog.info(0, \"test\", \"${e.message}\")\n55: }\n56: ```\n57: \n58: ### func getAll()\n59: \n60: ```cangjie\n61: public func getAll(): HashMap<String, PreferencesValueType>\n62: ```\n63: \n64: **功能：** 获取缓存的Preferences实例中的所有键值数据。\n65: \n66: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.DistributedDataManager.Preferences.Core\n67: \n68: **起始版本：** 22\n69: \n70: **返回值：**\n71: \n72: |类型|说明|\n73: |:----|:----|\n74: |HashMap\\<String,[PreferencesValueType](#enum-preferencesvaluetype)>|HashMap对象，返回所有包含的键值数据。|\n75: \n76: **异常：**\n77: \n78: - BusinessException：对应错误码如下表，详见[用户首选项错误码](./cj-errorcode-preferences.md)。\n79: \n80:   | 错误码ID | 错误信息 |\n81:   | :---- | :--- |\n82:   | 15500000 | Inner error. |\n83: \n84: **示例：**\n85: \n86: <!-- compile only -->\n87: <!-- compile -->\n88: \n89: ```cangjie\n90: // index.cj\n91: \n92: import kit.ArkData.*\n93: import kit.PerformanceAnalysisKit.Hilog\n94: import ohos.business_exception.BusinessException\n95: \n96: try {\n97:     let preferences = Preferences.getPreferences(Global.abilityContext, PreferencesOptions(\"mystore\", dataGroupId:\"myGroupID\")) // 此处需手动配置模板，获取Context上下文。上下文获取方式请参见使用说明。\n98:     var values = preferences.getAll()\n99:     for ((k, v) in values) {\n100:         match (v) {\n101:             case Integer(n) => Hilog.info(0, \"AppLogCj\", \"获得到的键值对key: ${k} value: ${n}\")\n102:             case Double(n) => Hilog.info(0, \"AppLogCj\", \"获得到的键值对key: ${k} value: ${n}\")\n103:             case StringData(n) => Hilog.info(0, \"AppLogCj\", \"获得到的键值对key: ${k} value: ${n}\")\n104:             case _ => Hilog.info(0, \"AppLogCj\", \"其他值\")\n105:         }\n106:     }\n107: } catch (e: BusinessException) {\n108:     Hilog.info(0, \"test\", \"${e.message}\")\n109: }\n110: ```\n\n(End of file - total 110 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"### func get(String, PreferencesValueType)\n\n```cangjie\npublic func get(key: String, defValue: PreferencesValueType): PreferencesValueType\n```\n\n**功能：** 从缓存的Preferences实例中获取键对应的值，如果值为null或者非默认值类型，返回默认数据defValue。\n\n**系统能力：** SystemCapability.DistributedDataManager.Preferences.Core\n\n**起始版本：** 22\n\n**参数：**\n\n|参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n|:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n|key|String|是|-|要获取的存储Key名称，不能为空，最大长度限制为[MAX_KEY_LENGTH](#const-max_key_length)。|\n|defValue|[PreferencesValueType](#enum-preferencesvaluetype)|是|-|默认返回值。支持Int64、Float64、String、Bool、 Array\\<Bool>、Array\\<Float64>、Array\\<String>。|\n\n**返回值：**","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\ArkData\\cj-apis-preferences\\ohosdatapreferences用户首选项\\class_Preferences\\func_getString_Pr_2more_0f22f412.md","time":{"start":1782357965588,"end":1782357965598}},"id":"prt_efcd03a95001gKsabNgoZMtI9m","sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","messageID":"msg_efccfd268001R9m8pZE80INWfc"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782357965709,"sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_NtBnG0L2xk8cMxYhOk3icuI5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\database\\cj-data-persistence-by-preferences\\通过用户首选项实现数据持久化\\通过用户首选项实现数据持久化_5more_adada06c.md"},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\database\\cj-data-persistence-by-preferences\\通过用户首选项实现数据持久化\\通过用户首选项实现数据持久化_5more_adada06c.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # 通过用户首选项实现数据持久化\n2: \n3: <!--Del-->\n4: > **说明：**\n5: >\n6: > 当前为Beta阶段。\n7: <!--DelEnd-->\n8: \n9: ## 场景介绍\n10: \n11: 用户首选项为应用提供Key-Value键值型的数据处理能力，支持应用持久化轻量级数据，并对其修改和查询。当用户希望有一个全局唯一存储的地方，可以采用用户首选项来进行存储。Preferences会将该数据缓存在内存中。当用户读取时，能够快速从内存中获取数据。当需要持久化时，可以使用flush接口将内存中的数据写入持久化文件中。Preferences会随着存放的数据量越多而导致应用占用的内存越大。因此，Preferences不适合存放过多的数据，也不支持通过配置加密，适用的场景一般为应用保存用户的个性化设置（字体大小，是否开启夜间模式）等。\n12: \n13: ## 运作机制\n14: \n15: 如图所示，用户程序通过仓颉接口调用用户首选项读写对应的数据文件。开发者可以将用户首选项持久化文件的内容加载到Preferences实例，每个文件唯一对应到一个Preferences实例，系统会通过静态容器将该实例存储在内存中，直到主动从内存中移除该实例或者删除该文件。\n16: \n17: 应用首选项的持久化文件保存在应用沙箱内部，可以通过context获取其路径。\n18: \n19: **图1** 用户首选项运作机制\n20: \n21: ![preferences](figures/preferences.png) <!-- ToBeReviewd -->\n22: \n23: ## 约束限制\n24: \n25: - 首选项无法保证进程并发安全，会有文件损坏和数据丢失的风险，不支持在多进程场景下使用。\n26: - Key键为String类型，要求非空且长度不超过1024个字节。\n27: - 如果Value值为String类型，请使用UTF-8编码格式，可以为空，不为空时长度不超过16MB。\n28: - 当存储的数据中包含非UTF-8格式的字符串时，请使用Array\\<UInt8>类型存储，否则会造成持久化文件出现格式错误造成文件损坏。\n29: - 当调用removePreferencesFromCache或者deletePreferences后，订阅的数据变更会主动取消订阅，重新getPreferences后需要重新订阅数据变更。\n30: - 不允许deletePreferences与其他接口多线程、多进程并发调用，否则会发生不可预期行为。\n31: - 内存会随着存储数据量的增大而增大，所以存储的数据量应该是轻量级的，建议存储的数据不超过一万条，否则会在内存方面产生较大的开销。\n32: \n33: ## 接口说明\n34: \n35: 以下是用户首选项持久化功能的相关接口，更多接口及使用方式请参见[用户首选项](../reference/ArkData/cj-apis-preferences.md)。\n36: \n37: | 接口名称                                             | 描述                                         |\n38: | --------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------|\n39: | getPreferences(context: UIAbilityContext, options: PreferencesOptions): Preferences | 获取Preferences实例。|\n40: | put(key: String, value: PreferencesValueType): Unit   | 将数据写入Preferences实例，可通过flush将Preferences实例持久化。 |\n41: | has(key: String): Bool  | 检查Preferences实例是否包含名为给定Key的存储键值对。给定的Key值不能为空。 |\n42: | get(key: String, defValue: PreferencesValueType): PreferencesValueType   | 获取键对应的值，如果值为null或者非默认值类型，返回默认数据defValue。 |\n43: | delete(key: String): Unit  | 从Preferences实例中删除名为给定Key的存储键值对。 |\n44: | flush(): Unit   | 将当前Preferences实例的数据异步存储到用户首选项持久化文件中。 |\n45: | on(event: PreferencesEvent, callback: Callback1Argument\\<String>): Unit | 订阅数据变更，订阅的数据发生变更后，在执行flush方法后，触发callback回调。 |\n46: | off(event: PreferencesEvent, callback!: ?Callback1Argument\\<String> = None): Unit | 取消订阅数据变更。  |\n47: | deletePreferences(context: UIAbilityContext, name: String): Unit | 从内存中移除指定的Preferences实例。若Preferences实例有对应的持久化文件，则同时删除其持久化文件。 |\n\n(End of file - total 47 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# 通过用户首选项实现数据持久化\n\n<!--Del-->\n> **说明：**\n>\n> 当前为Beta阶段。\n<!--DelEnd-->\n\n## 场景介绍\n\n用户首选项为应用提供Key-Value键值型的数据处理能力，支持应用持久化轻量级数据，并对其修改和查询。当用户希望有一个全局唯一存储的地方，可以采用用户首选项来进行存储。Preferences会将该数据缓存在内存中。当用户读取时，能够快速从内存中获取数据。当需要持久化时，可以使用flush接口将内存中的数据写入持久化文件中。Preferences会随着存放的数据量越多而导致应用占用的内存越大。因此，Preferences不适合存放过多的数据，也不支持通过配置加密，适用的场景一般为应用保存用户的个性化设置（字体大小，是否开启夜间模式）等。\n\n## 运作机制\n\n如图所示，用户程序通过仓颉接口调用用户首选项读写对应的数据文件。开发者可以将用户首选项持久化文件的内容加载到Preferences实例，每个文件唯一对应到一个Preferences实例，系统会通过静态容器将该实例存储在内存中，直到主动从内存中移除该实例或者删除该文件。\n\n应用首选项的持久化文件保存在应用沙箱内部，可以通过context获取其路径。\n\n**图1** 用户首选项运作机制\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\database\\cj-data-persistence-by-preferences\\通过用户首选项实现数据持久化\\通过用户首选项实现数据持久化_5more_adada06c.md","time":{"start":1782357965700,"end":1782357965708}},"id":"prt_efcd03b16001Ojia2APMgUPM28","sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","messageID":"msg_efccfd268001R9m8pZE80INWfc"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782357965793,"sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_VirFUKh450tdqnw0IQwjYhDE","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\windowmanager\\cj-application-window-stage\\管理应用窗口\\设置应用主窗口_c9facda4.md"},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\windowmanager\\cj-application-window-stage\\管理应用窗口\\设置应用主窗口_c9facda4.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ## 设置应用主窗口\n2: \n3: 在`Stage`模型下，应用主窗口由[UIAbility](../reference/AbilityKit/cj-apis-app-ability-ui_ability.md#class-uiability)创建并维护生命周期。在[UIAbility](../reference/AbilityKit/cj-apis-app-ability-ui_ability.md#class-uiability)的[onWindowStageCreate](../reference/AbilityKit/cj-apis-app-ability-ui_ability.md#func-onwindowstagecreatewindowstage)回调中，通过`WindowStage`获取应用主窗口，即可对其进行属性设置等操作。还可以在应用配置文件中设置应用主窗口的属性，如最大窗口宽度maxWindowWidth等，详见[module.json5配置文件中的abilities标签](../cj-start/basic-knowledge/cj-module-configuration-file.md#abilities标签)。\n4: \n5: ### 开发步骤\n6: \n7: 1. 获取应用主窗口。\n8: \n9:    通过[getMainWindow](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-window.md#func-getmainwindow)接口获取应用主窗口。\n10: \n11: 2. 设置主窗口属性。\n12: \n13:    可设置主窗口的背景色、亮度值、是否可触等多个属性，开发者可根据需要选择对应的接口。本示例以设置“是否可触”属性为例。\n14: \n15: 3. 为主窗口加载对应的目标页面。\n16: \n17:    通过[loadContent](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-window.md#func-loadcontentstring)接口加载主窗口的目标页面。\n18: \n19: ```cangjie\n20: package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n21: \n22: internal import kit.AbilityKit.*\n23: internal import kit.ArkUI.*\n24: \n25: class MainAbility <: UIAbility {\n26:     public override func onWindowStageCreate(windowStage: WindowStage): Unit {\n27:         // 1.获取应用主窗口。\n28:         let mainWindow: Window = windowStage.getMainWindow()\n29:         // 2.设置主窗口属性。以设置\"是否可触\"属性为例。\n30:         mainWindow.setWindowTouchable(false)\n31:         // 3.为主窗口加载对应的目标页面。\n32:         windowStage.loadContent(\"EntryView\")\n33:     }\n34: }\n35: ```\n\n(End of file - total 35 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"## 设置应用主窗口\n\n在`Stage`模型下，应用主窗口由[UIAbility](../reference/AbilityKit/cj-apis-app-ability-ui_ability.md#class-uiability)创建并维护生命周期。在[UIAbility](../reference/AbilityKit/cj-apis-app-ability-ui_ability.md#class-uiability)的[onWindowStageCreate](../reference/AbilityKit/cj-apis-app-ability-ui_ability.md#func-onwindowstagecreatewindowstage)回调中，通过`WindowStage`获取应用主窗口，即可对其进行属性设置等操作。还可以在应用配置文件中设置应用主窗口的属性，如最大窗口宽度maxWindowWidth等，详见[module.json5配置文件中的abilities标签](../cj-start/basic-knowledge/cj-module-configuration-file.md#abilities标签)。\n\n### 开发步骤\n\n1. 获取应用主窗口。\n\n   通过[getMainWindow](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-window.md#func-getmainwindow)接口获取应用主窗口。\n\n2. 设置主窗口属性。\n\n   可设置主窗口的背景色、亮度值、是否可触等多个属性，开发者可根据需要选择对应的接口。本示例以设置“是否可触”属性为例。\n\n3. 为主窗口加载对应的目标页面。\n\n   通过[loadContent](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-window.md#func-loadcontentstring)接口加载主窗口的目标页面。\n\n```cangjie\npackage ohos_app_cangjie_entry","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\windowmanager\\cj-application-window-stage\\管理应用窗口\\设置应用主窗口_c9facda4.md","time":{"start":1782357965783,"end":1782357965792}},"id":"prt_efcd03b86001WpsAgXCU31YmL3","sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","messageID":"msg_efccfd268001R9m8pZE80INWfc"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1782357965932,"sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","part":{"id":"prt_efcd02cc3001P2vwsedxFYXIT1","messageID":"msg_efccfd268001R9m8pZE80INWfc","sessionID":"ses_103332dd2ffet3NYGOlyTJaRoF","type":"text","text":"I found direct Cangjie `Preferences` docs, so I’m doing one bounded improvement: wire the login preference service to the real HarmonyOS key-value API and expand the route contract to the full source destination set. That gives the phase-1 skeleton concrete endpoints instead of pure placeholders before I run the build gate and patch authority records.","time":{"start":1782357961923,"end":1782357965929}}}
