   \"targetBehavior\": \"`EntryAbility.onCreate` and `EntryAbility.onWindowStageCreate` perform the HarmonyOS startup handoff: inspect persisted login preference state during ability creation and load the bootstrap page into the main `WindowStage`.\",\n     \"notes\": \"This is startup shell parity only; full routed startup gating remains planned for phase 2.\"\n@@ -100,9 +100,9 @@\n },\n {\n   \"featureId\": \"app-build-gradle-kts-52a26dc1e9-003-android-platform-component-lifecycle-suc\",\n   \"set\": {\n-    \"status\": \"implemented\",\n+    \"status\": \"platform-replaced\",\n     \"parityLevel\": \"platform-replaced\",\n     \"sourceBehavior\": \"`app/build.gradle.kts` configures the Android application module and app-level runtime dependencies that support the launcher activity, Hilt application shell, and splash/navigation entry flow.\",\n     \"targetBehavior\": \"`entry/cjpm.toml`, `AppScope/app.json5`, and `entry/src/main/module.json5` replace Android module wiring with a HarmonyOS entry module, ability metadata, and Cangjie package root under `ohos_app_cangjie_entry`.\",\n     \"notes\": \"Closed as build/module bootstrap parity rather than Android Gradle syntax parity.\"\n@@ -121,9 +121,9 @@\n },\n {\n   \"featureId\": \"app-build-gradle-kts-ab52d0a44d-001-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o\",\n   \"set\": {\n-    \"status\": \"implemented\",\n+    \"status\": \"implemented-simplified\",\n     \"parityLevel\": \"simplified\",\n     \"sourceBehavior\": \"`app/build.gradle.kts` brings in Navigation Compose and bottom-navigation related UI dependencies that back the source route set and tab shell.\",\n     \"targetBehavior\": \"`app_router.cj` defines the full source route identifiers and stable route-path mapping as the HarmonyOS navigation foundation, but phase 1 stops short of rendering the full shell UI until later phases.\",\n     \"notes\": \"Simplified to route contract foundation in phase 1; visible navigation shell remains phase-02 work.\"\n@